					 			 <div id="content" class="grid_6">												 
												 
												 <h1>List of Publications</h1>
												 
												 <div class="recent-posts">
												 			<h2>Main publications</h2>
												 			<ol>
												 			  <li><strong>Clustering Web Documents Using Co-citation, Coupling, Incoming, and Outgoing Hyperlinks: a Comparative Performance Analysis of Algorithms.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Stéphane Bressan. International Journal of Web Information System 2 (2), June 2006. <a href="IJWIS2-1-1Bressan.pdf">pdf</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Journey to the Centre of the Star: Various Ways of Finding Star Centers in Star Clustering.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Stéphane Bressan. R. Wagner, N. Revell, and G. Pernul (Eds.): DEXA 2007, LNCS 4653, pp. 660-670, 2007. <a href="WijayaBressan_starClusteringDEXA07.pdf">pdf</a> <a href="dexa07.ppt">slides</a> <a href="star.rar">codes</a> <a href="google.zip">data</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Hierarchical Clustering for POS Tagging of the Indonesian Language. </strong>Derry Tanti Wijaya and Stéphane Bressan. SNLP 2007. <a href="BressanWijaya_MSTClusteringSNLP07.pdf">pdf</a> <a href="snlp07.ppt">slides</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Random Walk on the Red Carpet: Rating Movies with User Reviews and PageRank.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Stéphane Bressan. CIKM 2008. <a href="BressanWijaya_cikm2008.pdf">pdf</a> <a href="CIKM2008.ppt">slides</a> <a href="opinionMining.rar">codes+data</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Ricochet: A Family of Unconstrained Algorithms for Graph clustering.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Stéphane Bressan. DASFAA 2009. <a href="BressanWijaya_RicochetClusteringDASFAA09.pdf">pdf</a> <a href="dasfaa09.ppt">slides</a> <a href="ricochet.rar">codes+data</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Predicting Classifier Performance Using Data Set Descriptors and Data Mining Ontology.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya, Alexandros Kalousis, Melanie Hilario. Proc. of the 3rd Planning to Learn Workshop, ECAI 2010.</li>
														 	  <li><strong>"Nut Case: What does It Mean?": Understanding Semantic Relationship between Nouns in Noun Compounds through Paraphrasing and Ranking the Paraphrases.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Philip Gianfortoni. Proc. of the Workshop on Search and Mining Entity-Relationship Data (SMER) 2011, CIKM 2011. <a href="http://rtw.ml.cmu.edu/papers/wijaya-smer11.pdf">pdf</a></li>
												 			  <li><strong>Understanding Semantic Change of Words Over Centuries.</strong> Derry Tanti Wijaya and Reyyan Yeniterzi. Proc. of the Workshop on Detecting and Exploiting Cultural Diversity on the Social Web (DETECT) 2011, CIKM 2011. <a href="http://rtw.ml.cmu.edu/papers/wijaya-detect11.pdf">pdf</a></li>

															  <li><strong>Clustering Vertices in Weighted Graphs.</strong>Derry Wijaya, . </li>
															  <li><strong>Coupled Temporal Scoping.</strong>Partha Pratim Talukdar, Derry Wijaya, Tom Mitchell. In Proceedings of the International Conference on Web Search and Data Mining (WSDM 2012), Seattle, USA. <a href="http://rtw.ml.cmu.edu/papers/talukdar-wsdm12.pdf">pdf</a></li>
															  <li><strong>Acquiring Temporal Constraints between Relations.</strong>Partha Pratim Talukdar, Derry Wijaya, Tom Mitchell. To appear in CIKM 2012, Hawaii, USA. <a href="http://rtw.ml.cmu.edu/papers/talukdar-cikm12.pdf">pdf</a></li>
									 			   </ol>
												 			<p>&nbsp;</p>
