												 			<h2>Other publications</h2>
						 			               <ol>
									 			              <li><strong>A Farmer's Hope</strong>. Derry Tanti Wijaya and Syahrial Dahler. An article in the book Gema Kebangkitan: Catatan Harapan Anak Bangsa (Echo of Awakening: Diary of Hopes from the Children of the Nation). A book published in celebration of the 100th-year Indonesian National Awakening day, 2008.  <a href="aFarmersHope.pdf">pdf</a></li>
									 			              <li><strong>The Role of Women in Local Economic Reform in Indonesia</strong>. Derry Tanti Wijaya. A research done for the Women Study Center, State University of Malang, Indonesia, 2003</li>
